    tmp = wp.abs(((v2 + 0.32 + v0 + 0.07) * tmp))
    v2 = wp.cos(v0)
    v0 = (wp.sin(wp.cos(v1 + 0.37)) - ((v0 + 0.08 - v2 + 0.63) - wp.exp(tmp + 0.76)))
    tmp = v2
    v2 = wp.abs(((v2 + 0.92 + v2 + 0.84) - wp.sin(tmp + 0.56)))
    tmp = (wp.cos(wp.sin(v1 + 0.88)) / wp.abs((v0 + 0.67 / v2 + 0.95)))
    tmp = (wp.abs(0.54) + wp.sin(wp.abs(v1 + 0.99)))
    data[tid] = v0
